        <hl1>Handley Needs A Break Today</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Sports Editor:</p>
        <p>I don't know whose ideas of justice are worse, Judge Roy Bean's or the average Giants fan's. Of Coach Ray Handley: Some Giants fans want him fired, others want to send him to law school (at their own expense, no less). I've got the best idea: How about giving him a break? JIM ENGLISH Bayside, Queens</p>
      </block>
